{
  "texts": [
    "Since there is little we can do to stop the use of chatbots in our courses [2], we advocate providing safe, course-aligned access to chatbots within our courses.",
    "Furthermore, we recognize that student data is confidential [3], so it is imperative that these chatbots be created with data privacy in mind.",
    "Therefore, we further advocate for local hosting of as much infrastructure as possible.Beyond privacy and course-alignment, local hosting has several benefits over using externally hosted chatbots.",
    "Admittedly, local hosting has logistical overhead that is not present when using an externally hosted chatbot.",
    "Indeed, with the advent of OpenAI's custom \"GPTs\" [4], much of the required functionality to produce a coursealigned, interactive chatbot can be outsourced to a hosting company."
  ]
}